author: Talia Kaplan
title: Peter Navarro: China 'cornered' the personal protective equipment market and 'is profiteering' during coronavirus outbreak
description: White House Trade Adviser Peter Navarro said during an exclusive interview on “Sunday Morning Futures” that China "cornered" the personal protective equipment (PPE) market during the coronavirus outbreak and “is profiteering.”
